    "id": "Account-Manager---The-Netherlands_25657",
    "title": "Account Manager - The Netherlands",
    "description": "<span><p><span>What if we told you that you can achieve more at TomTom in less time than at any other company?</span></p><p></p><p><span>From coding the next product revolution, to selling it, we always want inspired people to join us. </span></p><p></p><p><span>Find the right vacancy for you? Please click Apply.<span>&nbsp;</span>We look forward getting to know you!</span></p></span><p><b>Where do you want to be?</b></p><p></p><p>We are looking for the best and brightest minds to join our Benelux Sales team within our Telematics Unit. The experience and future opportunities will include:</p><p>Your primary purpose is to sale products and services of <b>TomTom Telematics in The Netherlands</b>. In cooperation with our marketing team and telemarketing organization you gain new customers and increase revenue and customer satisfaction. You are an experienced Account manager with a proven track record. You are a self-starting professional and an inspiration to your colleagues and customers.&nbsp;</p><p></p><p><b>In this position you will</b>….</p><ul><li>Reach outstanding sales results;</li><li>Use your industry knowledge to address new markets and customers and seek both traditional and creative ways to penetrate them;</li><li>Support the eco-system of software partners and integrators that can help promote TomTom Telematics&nbsp; and&nbsp; deliver end-to-end solutions to our customers;</li><li>Drive sales in selected vertical market sectors working closely with the marketing manager, sales engineer and technical teams;</li><li>Report directly into the Sales Director Benelux of TomTom Telematics.</li></ul><p></p><p><b>What do we expect from you?</b></p><p></p><p>To be successful in this role as an&nbsp;Account Manager for TomTom Telematics,&nbsp;this is the kind of profile we have in mind:&nbsp;</p><ul><li>Fluent in Dutch and English;</li><li>Minimum of 3-5 years of Sales experience with an outstanding sales track record;</li><li>A real sales hunter who enjoys closing deals;</li><li>Thorough understanding of the Dutch B2B market with a network of potential sales partners/prospects;</li><li>You enjoy challenges;</li><li>Driven and ambitious with real passion for our products and market.</li></ul><p></p><p><b>What do we offer?</b></p><p></p><p>An adventure in the cutting-edge field of telematics, digital mapping, traffic and navigation solutions; The chance to work in a fast moving, innovative and international environment, dealing with all kind of different countries and cultures; The opportunity to join a dynamic team where your contribution really makes a difference Contract with&nbsp;flexible benefits, flexible holiday plan, collective health insurance, and pension scheme.</p><p></p><p><b>Who are we?</b></p><p></p><p>Founded in 1991 and headquartered in Amsterdam, we have 4,700 employees worldwide and sell our products in over 36 countries.</p><p>Our business consists of four customer facing business units: Consumer, Automotive, Licensing and Telematics.</p><p>TomTom Telematics is a Business Unit of TomTom dedicated to fleet management, vehicle telematics and connected car services. WEBFLEET is a Software-as-a-Service solution, used by small to large businesses to improve vehicle performance, save fuel, support drivers and increase overall fleet efficiency. In addition, TomTom Telematics provides services for the insurance, rental and leasing industries, car importers and companies that address businesses as well as consumers.</p><p>TomTom Telematics is one of the world’s leading telematics solution providers with more than 696,000 subscriptions worldwide. The company services drivers in more than 60 countries, giving them the industry’s strongest local support network and widest range of sector-specific third party applications and integrations. More than 46,000 customers benefit every day from the high standards of confidentiality, integrity and availability of our ISO/IEC 27001:2013 certified service, re-audited in November 2016.</p><p>For further information, please visit <a href=\"http://tomtom.com/telematics\" target=\"_blank\">tomtom.com/telematics</a></p><p>Follow us on Twitter <a href=\"https://twitter.com/tomtomwebfleet\" target=\"_blank\">@TomTomWEBFLEET</a></p><p></p><p><b>Interested?</b></p><p></p><p>For the full story about the vacancy or procedure please click on <u>www.tomtom.com/careers</u> or for specific questions contact Cecilia Clech.</p><p>Pre-employment screening is part of the selection process.</p>",
