    "id": "Senior-Sales-Representative---Telematics_25434",
    "title": "Senior Sales Representative - Telematics",
    "description": "<p><span>TomTom Telematics is the fastest growing business unit within TomTom. It’s main SaaS platform WEBFLEET supports over 46.000 business customers worldwide to realize substantial operational performance improvement. With a strategy of indirect and direct sales as well as M&amp;A, TomTom Telematics grows with more than 30% yearly. Would you like to be part of a team that challenges itself to outperform daily and contribute to growing a new (SaaS for Business) market?</span></p><p><span>Where do you want to be…in a year, in 5 years?</span><br><span>What if you had the opportunity to achieve more in less time then you could ever imagine?</span><br><br><span>At TomTom, you can.&nbsp;</span><br><br><span>We are looking for the best and brightest minds to join our <b><b>Telematics</b></b> team to support our growth strategy for the future. This is an incredibly exciting opportunity to join us in a state of rapid growth. Big things are happening and we are seeking for <b>Senior</b> <b><b>Sales&nbsp;&nbsp;Representative </b></b>for <b><b>Mexico City</b></b> with the possibility to travel around Mexico 2 days/week.</span><br><br><b><span><b>Sound good so far?</b></span></b>&nbsp;<br><br><span>Here’s a little taste of your challenge:</span></p><ul><li>Work with your team to reach outstanding sales results</li><li>Use your extensive industry knowledge to address new markets and seek both traditional and creative ways to penetrate them</li><li>Create a loyalty, committed, and consistently performing sales partner channels</li><li>Manage, coach, supervise and mentor the existing internal sales teams</li><li>Develop and manage KPI’ s to drive appropriate individual and team behavior</li><li>Lead by example and coach your sales team members to become more effective with customers/prospects by emphasizing good sales process methods;</li><li>Be actively involved in managing marketing activities together with the marketing team</li></ul><p></p><p>As a member of this team, you will be asked to deliver the following:</p><p></p><ul><li>Manage the sales&nbsp;through different channels and thanks to your network.</li><li>Manage to establish sustainable partnerships.</li><li>Contribute actively to the customers, resellers and partners’ satisfaction.</li><li>Leverage the network and cultivate the existing interpersonal relationships.</li></ul><p></p><p><b><span><b>What we are looking for:</b></span></b></p><ul><li>You have a Bachelor degree.</li><li>You have minimum of 4- 6 years of experience in a similar role</li><li>You have a Track Record in direct sales and&nbsp;channel management</li><li>Clear passion for an innovation driven market, like Telematics, Automotive, Mobile or IT;</li><li>You are fluent in English and Spanish;</li><li>You have outstanding leadership, management, problem solving and interpersonal skills;</li><li>You are an excellent Networker and Self-Starter.</li></ul><p></p><p><b><span><b>What you can expect:</b></span></b></p><p>- A very exciting role in the cutting-edge field of Telematics (more than 30% of annual growth);</p><p>- &nbsp;The chance to work in a fast moving, innovative and international environment, dealing with all kind of different countries and cultures;</p><p>- Interesting contract and commission scheme.</p><p><br><b><span><b>Want to join us?</b></span></b></p><p><br><span>We would like to meet you!</span></p><p></p><p><span>For the full story about the vacancy or procedure, please click on&nbsp;tomtom.com/careers</span></p><p><span>Pre-employment screening is part of the selection process.&nbsp;</span></p>",
