    "id": "Tester-for-Autonomous-Driving-Team_25458-1",
    "title": "Tester for Autonomous Driving Team",
    "description": "<p>Where do you want to be…in a year, in 5 years?</p><p>What if you had the opportunity to achieve more in less time then you could ever imagine?</p><p>At TomTom, you can.</p><p>Did you know that TomTom had Mobile Mapping technology 5 years before Google? At TomTom we capture petabytes of data with our vans driving across the world. We collect imagery, laser point clouds, inertial data and other sensor output.</p><p>We are looking for a person who will be responsible for coordination of Software Engineers to deliver high quality products through implementation of properly designed test scenarios.</p><p><b>Sound good so far?</b></p><p><b>Here’s a little taste of your challenge:</b></p><ul><li>Do you need to quickly view how the street looks like in any part of collected world?</li><li>Do you want to automatically recognize all road signs placed along the road from Berlin to Paris?</li><li>Do you want to fully reconstruct 3D model of million kilometers of highways in Europe?</li><li>You’ve got it! Such kind of problems is what our team deals with regularly.</li></ul><p><b>Where do you want to be?</b></p><p>We are looking for the best and brightest minds in engineering who will design and build scalable data processing systems in highly innovative area of business.</p><ul><li>If you have ever asked yourself how big IT players build their systems</li><li>If you are curious how petabytes of data are organized to be useful</li><li>If you are interested in computer vision or signal processing</li><li>If you&nbsp; want to see how cars scan 3D world with laser sensors</li><li>If you are interested in distributed services or cloud computing</li><li>Or maybe you love math and algorithms</li><li>If you want to take part in building new, innovative software</li><li>If you want to change the world (or just have a good time trying…)</li></ul><p>&nbsp;…then wait no more. Join our team and see it live on the job.</p><p></p><p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=86U4sxCpRf8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=86U4sxCpRf8</a></p><p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=38y1RT2p16w\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=38y1RT2p16w</a></p><p></p><p><b>What we are looking for:</b></p><p>To be successful in this role, this is the kind of profile we have in mind:</p><ul><li>Basic programing and automation background</li><li>Knowledge of testing methods</li><li>Open mind and readiness to discuss, question and propose new ideas in order to build state-of-the-art system</li><li>Readiness to learn and teach others</li><li>Good command of English language</li></ul><p><b>What you can expect</b></p><ul><li>You will never get bored! We move fast like a “start-up” but have the benefits of a billion euro company.</li><li>A company culture that likes to work hard and play hard. We like to have fun. There is no sense coming to a job everyday if you don’t like the people you work with.</li><li>Have an idea? A suggestion? A new way of doing something? The founders are still very present in the company and are very accessible. We all are. There is always room for good ideas. Entrepreneurialism is valued.</li><li>Decisive actions. We don’t like to wait. It’s in our DNA to move forward. So it only makes sense that we don’t jam the company with lots of layers. We make things happen. Quickly.</li><li>Let’s not forget the good stuff: flexible benefits (including multisport card), private medical care, 50% product discount and bonus scheme.</li></ul><p><b>Want to join us?</b></p><p><b>We would like to meet you!</b></p><p>For the full story about the vacancy or procedure, please click on <a href=\"http://www.tomtom.com/careers\" target=\"_blank\">www.tomtom.com/careers</a> or contact Marta Brzeszczynska.</p><p>We kindly ask you to complete the form and attachments in English.</p><p>Pre-employment screening of all external candidates is part of the selection process.</p>",
