    "title": "iOS Software Engineer",
    "description": "<p>Our team <b>achieves more</b> every day. So can you.</p><p></p><p>We have been making navigation apps since 2008 and have been the market leader ever since. And, we are not slowing down. &nbsp;</p><ul><li>Do you take your mobile device everywhere and instead of sharing photos you share Objective-C?</li><li>Would you like to take on the challenge to work on a complex and large iOS App</li><li>Do you like working on next generation technologies? Who doesn’t actually?</li><li>What about making a difference with your OWN ideas for features and improvements, getting a top place on the backlog?</li></ul><p></p><p><b>Sound interesting?</b></p><p></p><p>How about - <b>Want to code the future?</b></p><p>Pretty big thinking. We like to think we make that happen.</p><p>We are looking for product-aware engineers who have a passion for building applications that drive the future of navigation and beyond.&nbsp;&nbsp; Designing and developing the best possible products is what we're famous for!</p><p></p><p><span><b>Here’s a little taste of your challenge</b></span></p><ul><li>Build compelling new user experiences within TomTom’s iOS apps</li><li>Work on next gen technologies: – screen replication, advanced car integration, hybrid navigation, cloud integration, deep phone OS integration and using latest API from iOS.</li><li>Craft new and improved features and create engaging experiences.</li><li>Use motion and animation to bring delight to interactions.</li><li>Move the app forward rapidly, while sweating the details.</li></ul><p></p><p><span><b>What we expect from you</b></span></p><ul><li>Top-notch C++ and Objective-C and engineering know how (and a desire to keep learning).</li><li>Knowledge of iOS development tools is a plus.</li><li>You like to work as part of a self-organizing Scrum team in a scaled agile framework.</li><li>BS or MS in Computer Science or equivalent work experience. But if you're talented, degrees aren’t everything.</li></ul><p></p><p><span><b>What you can expect from us</b></span></p><ul><li>You will never get bored!&nbsp; We move fast like a “start-up” but have the benefits of a billion euro company.</li><li>A company culture that likes to work hard and play hard.&nbsp; We like to have fun.&nbsp; There is no sense coming to a job everyday if you don’t like the people you work with.</li><li>Have an idea? A suggestion? A new way of doing something?&nbsp; The founders are still very present in the company and are very accessible.&nbsp; We all are.&nbsp; There is always room for good ideas.&nbsp; Entrepreneurialism is valued.</li><li>Decisive actions.&nbsp; We don’t like to wait.&nbsp; It’s in our DNA to move forward.&nbsp; So it only makes sense that we don’t jam the company with lots of layers.&nbsp; We make things happen.&nbsp; Quickly.</li><li>Amsterdam.&nbsp; A pretty cool city to live and work. Lots of inspiration and when it’s sunny, the whole city comes alive!</li></ul>",
