    "description": "<p><span><span><span><span>Our team<span>&nbsp;</span><b>achieves more</b><span>&nbsp;</span>every day. So can you.<br>At TomTom we have some of the largest labelled maps-related databases in the world.<br>This puts us in a unique position to advance highly automated driving and impact the future of driving.<br><br><b>Your opportunity</b><br>We are seeking a computer vision and machine learning R&amp;D engineer for our Autonomous Driving team.<br>From TomTom’s headquarters in Amsterdam, you are researching world class algorithms and models to innovate our map technology for self-driving cars, and to automatically extract features relevant for autonomous driving.<br>Why you would love to work with us:</span></span></span></span></p><ul><li><span><span><span><span>You will work together with professionals in an open, friendly environment where creativity is key</span></span></span></span></li><li><span><span><span><span>We are close to the research community and work on cutting edge algorithms and models</span></span></span></span></li><li><span><span><span><span>We are passionate about our work, and take ownership of and pride in what we do and achieve</span></span></span></span></li><li><span><span><span><span>You will have access to huge amount of labelled maps-related databases</span></span></span></span></li><li><span><span><span><span>Your innovative solutions will be put to practice, changing people’s everyday lives</span></span></span></span></li></ul><p><br><span><span><span><span><b>What we expect from you</b></span></span></span></span></p><ul><li><span><span><span><span>Solid academic background in computer vision and machine learning with a postgraduate degree</span></span></span></span></li><li><span><span><span><span>Proven practical experience with relevant topics in computer vision and machine learning</span></span></span></span></li><li><span><span><span><span>Experience with deep learning frameworks such as Caffe, Torch or TensorFlow</span></span></span></span></li><li><span><span><span><span>Expert knowledge of modern C++ and proficiency in Python</span></span></span></span></li><li><span><span><span><span>Top-notch programming skills and software engineering know-how, and a desire to keep learning</span></span></span></span></li><li><span><span><span><span>Ability to write clean, elegant and maintainable production-level code</span></span></span></span></li><li><span><span><span><span>Creative problem solver and team player with strong conceptual skills</span></span></span></span></li><li><span><span><span><span>Highly motivated to work in a research and prototyping environment, and to be getting your work into production</span></span></span></span></li><li><span><span><span><span>Ability to work well with others; TomTom is a collaborative environment</span></span></span></span></li><li><span><span><span><span>Active participation in our scientific reading group</span></span></span></span></li><li><span><span><span><span>Self-motivated and dedicated to excellence</span></span></span></span></li><li><span><span><span><span>Fluency in English</span></span></span></span></li></ul><p><br><span><span><span><span><b>Being such an innovative position, preferably you also have</b></span></span></span></span></p><ul><li><span><span><span><span>A strong publication record with the top-tier computer vision and machine learning conferences and journals</span></span></span></span></li><li><span><span><span><span>Prior experience in Automotive R&amp;D</span></span></span></span></li><li><span><span><span><span>Prior experience with LIDAR and Radar data</span></span></span></span></li><li><span><span><span><span>Prior experience with programming resource-constrained platforms (e.g. embedded or mobile)</span></span></span></span></li><li><span><span><span><span>Prior experience with GPU programming (CUDA, OpenCL)</span></span></span></span></li></ul><p><br><span><span><span><span><b>Want to join us?</b><br><i>We would like to meet you!</i><br>Please apply through<span>&nbsp;</span><a href=\"http://www.tomtom.com/careers\" target=\"_blank\">www.tomtom.com/careers</a>.<br><br>We kindly ask you to complete the form and attachments in English.<br>Pre-employment screening of all external candidates is part of the selection process.</span></span></span></span></p>",
