    "id": "Online-Marketing-Manager-B2B---UKI---US---Telematics_25435-5",
    "title": "Online Marketing Manager B2B - UKI & US - Telematics",
    "description": "<p></p><p><span>TomTom Telematics is one of the world’s leading telematics solution providers with more than 700,000 subscriptions worldwide. The company services drivers in more than 60 countries, giving them the industry’s strongest local support network and widest range of sector-specific third party applications and integrations. More than 46,000 customers benefit every day from the high standards of confidentiality, integrity and availability of our ISO/IEC 27001 certified service</span><span>, re-audited in November 2016</span>.</p><p></p><p><b>Where do you want to be?</b></p><p></p><p>We are looking for the best and brightest minds in online marketing to become part of our online team. This position is a great opportunity for an experienced and data-driven B2B online marketing manager who is looking to take his/ her career to the next level.</p><p>You will be responsible for all our online -and lead generation activities in both the UKI and US. This involves budget planning, strategy, agency management and the timely and qualitative execution of your plans. In this role you will report to the European Digital Marketing Manager. The role includes:</p><p></p><ul><li>Create yearly online marketing plans for your regions and realize herein defined KPI’s.</li><li>Initiate creative and effective online marketing campaigns including, but not limited to <b>marketing automation</b>, <b>SEA</b>, <b>SEO</b>, <b>display</b> and <b>remarketing</b>.</li><li>Use marketing automation to actively acquire and create warm leads and nurture the prospect database.</li><li>Optimize conversion of online ads and campaign landing pages.</li><li>Grow the contribution of inbound marketing as the most cost effective and cost efficient tool for lead generation.</li><li>Translate data into meaningful information, monitor and report on lead generation and campaign performance towards key stakeholders in (tele)marketing and sales.</li><li>Manage local online lead generation budget, propose how to effectively distribute this over the available online channels.</li><li>Actively manage local digital agencies and external lead providers.</li></ul><p></p><p><b>What do we expect from you?</b></p><p></p><p>To be successful as an Online Marketing Manager, this is the kind of profile we have in mind:</p><ul><li>Keywords that describe you well: results oriented, takes initiative, creative, data driven, good communicator, positive attitude.</li><li>Minimum of 5 years work experience in online marketing and lead generation in a B2B environment.</li><li>Fully proficient in <b>Marketing Automation</b>, incl lead scoring models and user flows. Hands on experience with platforms like <b>Eloqua, Hubspot</b> or <b>Marketo</b>.</li><li>Good knowledge of<b> Google Analytics,&nbsp;Adwords </b>and<b> SEO </b>techniques.</li><li>Ability to initiate, prioritize and manage multiple demanding projects in a fast paced, constantly changing environment.</li><li>Strong analytical skills, understand how to gather data and turn it into actions to improve online performance. Able to analyze the prospects behavior and delivers content at the right time.</li><li>Proven track record of developing successful creative B2B campaigns.</li><li>Strong independent contributor – that excels in a team – and brings that team steps further</li><li>Extensive experience managing online agencies and budgets.</li><li>English native speaker.</li><li>Experience in a fast-paced, dynamic, multi-cultural and international environment is an advantage.</li><li>Willingness to travel.</li></ul><p></p><p><b>What do we offer?</b></p><p></p><ul><li>An adventure in the cutting-edge field of telematics, digital mapping, traffic and navigation solutions;</li><li>The chance to work in a fast moving, innovative and international environment, dealing with all kind of different countries and cultures;</li><li>The opportunity to join a dynamic team where your contribution really makes a difference;</li><li>Contract with flexible benefits, flexible holiday plan, collective health insurance, and pension scheme.</li></ul><p></p><p><b>Interested?</b></p><p></p><p>For the full story about the vacancy or procedure, please click on <a href=\"http://www.tomtom.com/careers\" target=\"_blank\">www.tomtom.com/careers</a>&nbsp;or for specific questions contact Jana Zaremba.</p><p></p><p>Pre-employment screening is part of the selection process.</p>",
