    "title": "Software Engineer Intern",
    "description": "<p></p><p><b>Software Engineer Intern </b></p><p></p><p><b>About TomTom </b></p><p>In Traffic and Travel Information Product Department we process traffic data as well as data from speed cameras and other data related to travelling. Our web platform allows users to analyze and monitor traffic on the road network worldwide. We also create moderation tools, marketing applications, and more.</p><p>Visit out TomTom City web page here: http://city.tomtom.com.</p><p></p><p><b>What we use: </b></p><p> Java and Spring in back-end</p><p> React JS, Sass and Webpack in front-end</p><p> Amazon, Docker and Azure in deployments</p><p> Jira, Confluence and Bitbucket in daily work organization</p><p></p><p><b>What we expect from you: </b></p><p> Student in a field of Computer Science or any IT background (at UŁor PŁ</p><p> Positive attitude and analytical mind</p><p> Ability to think out of the box and bring new ideas to the table</p><p> Programming basics</p><p> Basic English</p><p></p><p><b>More than welcome: </b></p><p> Knowledge of JAVA, JS, CSS, HTML, AWS, GIT, LINUX</p><p></p><p><b>What we offer: </b></p><p> Paid internship with flexible working time</p><p> The possibility to deliver real business value</p><p> Experienced engineers to work with and learn from</p><p> Friendly working atmosphere</p><p> Access to foosball, billiard table and darts</p><p></p><p><b>Interested? </b></p><p><i>We would like to meet you! </i></p><p>To apply, please click on www.tomtom.com/careers or contact Justyna Sobótka (Justyna.Sobotka@tomtom.com)</p>",
